com.illposed.osc

Class OSCMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.illposed.osc.AbstractOSCPacket
      • com.illposed.osc.OSCMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OSCPacket

    public class OSCMessage
extends AbstractOSCPacket
    An simple (non-bundle) OSC message. An OSC Message is made up of an Address Pattern (the receiver of the message) and Arguments (the content of the message).

      • ILLEGAL_ADDRESS_CHAR

        private static final java.util.regex.Pattern ILLEGAL_ADDRESS_CHAR
        Java regular expression pattern matching a single invalid character. The invalid characters are: ' ', '#', '*', ',', '?', '[', ']', '{', '}'
